    "Name": "Quark F",
    "Details": "The F configuration, introduced in 3070 by Clan Star Adder, builds around a Heavy Large Laser in the right arm as its primary long-range weapon. Four ER Micro Lasers distributed across the right torso and head provide close-range coverage, while twin AP Gauss Rifles in the left arm backed by a ton of ammunition make the F exceptionally dangerous to battle armor and conventional infantry. Heat management is demanding under sustained fire.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Improved Communications</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 0.98</color></b>",
